To upgrade OLAS from verion 2.2.1 to version 2.3:

- The directory 2014XXXXXXXXXX should be placed under the existing
  releases directory

- Verify that the symbolic link for log/ resolves to the shared/log/ directory

- Verify that the file config/databases.yml resolves to the existing version
  in the shared/config/ directory

- Apply the database updates

  ./scripts/update_2.3.sh

- Change the symbolic link "current" to point to releases/2014XXXXXXXXXX
